{#
name: Approval Flow
description: Multi-stage approval workflow with configurable approvers and timeout
tags: [workflow, approval, stages]
parameters:
  - name: skill_name
    type: str
    description: Skill display name
    required: true
  - name: skill_description
    type: str
    description: Brief description of approval flow purpose
    required: true
  - name: approval_stages
    type: str
    description: Comma-separated stage names (e.g. draft,review,final)
    required: true
  - name: approvers
    type: str
    description: Comma-separated approver identifiers per stage
    required: true
  - name: timeout
    type: int
    description: Timeout in hours for each stage
    default: 24
examples:
  - "Two-stage approval: draft -> review -> final"
#}
---
name: {{ skill_name | kebab_case }}
description: {{ skill_description }}
metadata:
  author: owlclaw
  version: "1.0"
owlclaw:
  spec_version: "1.0"
  task_type: workflow
---
# {{ skill_name }} — 使用指南

## 目标

{{ skill_description }}

## 审批阶段

- 阶段：{{ approval_stages }}
- 审批人：{{ approvers }}
- 每阶段超时：{{ timeout }} 小时

## 流程逻辑

1. 按 approval_stages 顺序推进
2. 每阶段由对应 approvers 审批
3. 超时未审批则触发提醒或自动处理

## 注意事项

- approval_stages 与 approvers 需一一对应
- timeout 单位为小时
